-- ── hume-ai → automation-agents ─────────────────────────────
('Hume AI', 'hume-ai', 'Empathic voice AI platform — EVI speech-to-speech, Octave TTS, and emotion-aware expression measurement APIs.', 'Hume AI builds voice and emotion AI infrastructure with a distinguishing thesis: empathic interfaces that understand and respond to emotional tone, not just words. The product line covers EVI (Empathic Voice Interface — closed-source speech-to-speech with interruption handling and back-channeling), Octave (closed-source LLM TTS with voice design, modulation, cloning, and conversion), TADA (open-source LLM TTS that streams text and audio together to reduce hallucinations), and Expression Measurement (emotional intelligence analysis across 48+ emotions and 600+ voice descriptors). Curated speech datasets across 50+ languages and 10+ domains support training and benchmarking. Hume''s positioning is the empathic-AI niche that ElevenLabs (voice cloning, no emotion-aware turn-taking), OpenAI Realtime API (voice, no expression measurement), Cartesia (low-latency TTS, no emotion layer), Vapi (voice agent infra), and Retell (voice agent platform) don''t cover natively.', 'https://www.hume.ai', 'freemium', '[]'::jsonb, 'intermediate', true, '{"web","api"}', '{"EVI — Empathic Voice Interface (speech-to-speech with interruptibility)","Octave — closed-source LLM text-to-speech with voice cloning","TADA — open-source LLM TTS streaming text + audio","Expression Measurement — 48+ emotions, 600+ voice descriptors","Curated speech datasets — 50+ languages, 10+ domains","Human Feedback API with science-backed survey templates","Conversational audio datasets with multi-speaker dynamics","Domain-specific training data (healthcare, finance)","RESTful API for study management"}', '{"OpenAI","Anthropic","Twilio","Webhooks","REST API"}', true, '{"Voice-AI builders needing emotion-aware turn-taking and back-channeling","Empathic-interface use cases (mental health, coaching, support) where tone matters","Researchers needing labeled emotion datasets across 50+ languages","Teams replacing ElevenLabs when expression nuance is more important than voice cloning"}', '{"Pure voice cloning use cases — ElevenLabs is cheaper and deeper","Real-time agent telephony at lowest possible latency (use Cartesia or Vapi)","Standard TTS for narration / audiobooks (overkill for non-conversational use)","Buyers wanting clear public pricing tiers (Hume''s pricing is API-first usage-based)"}', 'The empathic-voice specialist for builders who need expression-aware turn-taking, not just voice cloning — Hume''s EVI handles interruption + back-channeling natively in a way ElevenLabs and Cartesia don''t. The Expression Measurement API is genuinely unique. It''s weaker than ElevenLabs on voice cloning quality and ecosystem breadth, weaker than Vapi/Retell on agent-platform polish, and the usage-based pricing without clear tier $/mo creates budget uncertainty. Pick Hume when emotional nuance is core to the product (mental health, coaching, character voice); skip if you just need TTS narration.', now()),

-- ── synthflow-ai → automation-agents ────────────────────────
('Synthflow AI', 'synthflow-ai', 'Enterprise no-code voice AI agent platform for inbound and outbound calls — visual flow designer with in-house telephony.', 'Synthflow is a no-code voice AI platform for inbound and outbound phone-call automation. The Visual Flow Designer lets non-technical teams build agents handling appointment booking, lead qualification, customer support, and complex call routing through a drag-and-drop builder rather than prompts alone. Custom in-house telephony infrastructure delivers sub-100ms latency without third-party carrier dependency, plus BYOC (bring-your-own-carrier) support. AI Sandbox + Version Control let teams test and deploy without downtime. Real-Time Monitoring and Auto-QA analyze every call live. Multi-agent architecture supports complex enterprise workflows with specialized subflow agents. Omnichannel covers voice, SMS, WhatsApp, and chat. Compliance-certified for SOC 2, HIPAA, PCI DSS, and GDPR. Synthflow positions against Bland.ai, Vapi, Retell (third-party-carrier voice infra), Air.ai (AI sales calling), and ElevenLabs Voice AI (voice-as-feature, no agent platform).', 'https://www.synthflow.ai', 'paid', '[]'::jsonb, 'intermediate', true, '{"web","api"}', '{"Visual Flow Designer — drag-and-drop call logic builder","Custom in-house telephony — sub-100ms latency, BYOC support","AI Sandbox and Version Control for safe deployments","Real-Time Monitoring + Auto-QA call analysis","Multi-agent architecture for complex workflows","Omnichannel — voice, SMS, WhatsApp, chat","SOC 2 / HIPAA / PCI DSS / GDPR compliance","200+ partner integrations (CRM / ERP / CCaaS)","BELL deployment framework (Build, Evaluate, Launch, Learn)","Forward-deployed engineers for 60-day ROI"}', '{"HubSpot","Salesforce","Zapier","GoHighLevel","Cal.com","Twilio (BYOC)"}', true, '{"Mid-market and enterprise teams automating phone-call workflows","Compliance-bound industries needing SOC 2 / HIPAA / PCI DSS voice AI","Sales teams running outbound qualification and inbound call handling","Buyers who need a visual builder rather than prompt-engineering tooling"}', '{"Hobbyists and tinkerers (Bland.ai or Vapi DIY routes are cheaper)","Teams wanting open-source self-host (Synthflow is closed managed)","Workloads where speed-to-prototype matters more than enterprise polish","Buyers wanting predictable per-minute pricing visible up-front (PAYG, no public tier $)"}', 'The enterprise-grade voice AI agent platform for teams that have outgrown Bland.ai or Vapi and need real compliance, telephony control, and a visual builder non-engineers can use. Synthflow''s in-house telephony stack and SOC 2 / HIPAA / PCI DSS posture are the differentiators against the DIY voice agent crowd. It''s weaker than Bland.ai on price-per-minute for simple workloads, weaker than Vapi on developer ergonomics, and the no-public-pricing posture is a real friction. Pick Synthflow for compliance-bound enterprise deployments; skip it for hobbyist or sub-1K-call/month projects.', now()),

-- ── manychat → marketing-seo ────────────────────────────────
('ManyChat', 'manychat', 'AI chat marketing platform — Instagram DM, WhatsApp, Messenger, SMS, and Telegram automation for creators and ecommerce.', 'ManyChat is the dominant chat marketing platform for Instagram DM, WhatsApp, Messenger, SMS, Telegram, and TikTok automation — used by 1M+ businesses for lead capture, conversational commerce, and post-purchase flows. The product is built around a visual flow builder that triggers on keywords, story replies, post comments, ads, or QR codes; AI Step adds GPT-style intent detection and natural responses inside flows; templated growth tools cover comment-to-DM, story-mention auto-reply, and ad-to-DM lead capture. Native ecommerce integrations with Shopify and Klaviyo route conversation outcomes into orders, segments, and abandoned-cart flows without Zapier glue. ManyChat positions against Tidio (web-first chat), Drift / Intercom (B2B SaaS), Sendpulse (legacy ESP + chatbot), and Customers.ai (lead-data overlap). The differentiator is depth on creator-economy and ecommerce social-channel automation, where ManyChat''s post-comment + story-reply triggers are best-in-class.', 'https://manychat.com', 'freemium', '[{"plan":"Free","price":"$0","features":["Up to 1,000 contacts","Instagram DM, Messenger, WhatsApp basics","2 keyword triggers","Basic Flow Builder","ManyChat branding"]},{"plan":"Pro","price":"From $15/mo (scales by contacts)","features":["Unlimited contacts (paid by tier)","All channels","Unlimited keywords","Growth tools (comment-to-DM, story reply, ads)","No ManyChat branding","Integrations","AI Step (GPT-powered intent)"]},{"plan":"Premium","price":"Contact sales","features":["High-volume sending","Dedicated support","Multi-team workspaces","Advanced analytics","Custom integrations"]}]'::jsonb, 'beginner', true, '{"web","api"}', '{"Instagram DM automation (comment-to-DM, story reply, ads)","WhatsApp Business API automation","Facebook Messenger flows","SMS marketing automation","Telegram bot automation","TikTok DM automation (newer)","Visual Flow Builder with keyword triggers","AI Step — GPT-style intent detection inside flows","Templates for ecommerce, lead-capture, post-purchase","Live Chat handoff to human agents"}', '{"Shopify","Klaviyo","Mailchimp","HubSpot","Stripe","Google Sheets","Zapier","Make","ConvertKit","ActiveCampaign"}', true, '{"Creators and influencers running Instagram DM lead capture and product launches","Ecommerce brands automating post-purchase, abandoned-cart, and review-collection flows","Course / coaching businesses qualifying leads via comment-to-DM funnels","Small-to-mid social-first businesses on Meta + WhatsApp"}', '{"B2B SaaS sales teams (Drift / Intercom fit better)","Web-chat-first support workflows (Tidio is purpose-built)","Email-marketing-only stacks (use Klaviyo / Mailchimp directly)","Buyers needing fully self-hosted / open-source automation"}', 'The default chat marketing platform for creators and ecommerce brands running Instagram DM and WhatsApp automation in 2026 — ManyChat owns the comment-to-DM, story-reply, and ads-to-DM growth motions in a way no general chatbot platform replicates. AI Step adds usable GPT intent detection inside the same visual builder. It''s weaker than Tidio on web-chat support, weaker than Drift / Intercom on B2B SaaS workflows, and the contacts-based pricing scales fast on viral campaigns. Pick ManyChat if your funnel runs through Instagram DMs or WhatsApp; skip if your customers don''t live on social DMs.', now()),

-- ── laxis → sales ───────────────────────────────────────────
('Laxis', 'laxis', 'AI sales meeting and conversation copilot — capture, transcribe, summarize, and sync to CRM automatically.', 'Laxis is an AI conversation platform for sales meetings, customer interviews, and voice-driven productivity. Meeting Capture covers bot-free recording, AI assistant invitations, and uploaded audio/video; Intelligent Summaries generate structured notes with decisions, action items, and topic extraction; AI Chat Search lets users query meeting history across the entire archive; Voice Keyboard adds native dictation across any app (Slack, Gmail, Teams) with verbal cleanup. Automated CRM sync routes outcomes into HubSpot or Salesforce without manual data entry. 50+ professional report templates cover sales call summaries, customer interviews, and standups. Laxis positions against Gong and Chorus (enterprise revenue intelligence), Fireflies and Otter (transcription-first), Fathom and Grain (meeting recording with summaries). The differentiator is voice-first input + Voice Keyboard adjacent functionality, plus the device ecosystem (AI Earbuds, 360 camera) for offline / mobile capture beyond standard Zoom integrations.', 'https://www.laxis.com', 'freemium', '[]'::jsonb, 'beginner', false, '{"web","mobile"}', '{"Bot-free meeting capture and recording","AI-generated meeting summaries with action items","AI Chat Search across entire meeting archive","Voice Keyboard — native dictation in any app with cleanup","CRM auto-sync (HubSpot, Salesforce)","50+ report templates (sales, interview, standup)","Real-time meeting guidance and prompts","Team workspaces for shared archives","AI Earbuds and 360 camera ecosystem (mobile capture)"}', '{"HubSpot","Salesforce","Zoom","Google Meet","Microsoft Teams","Slack","Gmail","Notion","Microsoft Word","Zapier"}', true, '{"Sales reps logging meeting notes + auto-syncing to CRM","Customer success and discovery teams running structured interviews","Solo founders and consultants needing voice-first productivity","Mobile-heavy users capturing conversations outside standard video calls"}', '{"Enterprise revenue intelligence buyers (Gong / Chorus deeper)","Transcription-only workflows where Otter / Fireflies are cheaper","Teams without HubSpot or Salesforce — CRM sync is the killer feature","Buyers wanting full call-coaching scoring (Gong / Chorus / Spiky fit better)"}', 'A voice-first sales meeting copilot for SDRs and account executives who want CRM-synced meeting notes without standing up Gong-grade revenue intelligence. Laxis''s Voice Keyboard and 50+ report templates are genuinely useful productivity adds beyond standard transcription. It''s weaker than Gong on call-coaching depth, weaker than Otter on pure transcription pricing, and the device ecosystem (AI Earbuds, 360 camera) is novel but unnecessary for most users. Pick Laxis when CRM auto-sync is the bottleneck; skip if you need scored call coaching or you''re not on HubSpot / Salesforce.', now())

ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;

INSERT INTO tool_categories (tool_id, category_id)
SELECT t.id, c.id FROM tools t JOIN categories c ON c.slug = 'automation-agents' WHERE t.slug = 'hume-ai'      ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
